BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-dplyr 
BuildRequires:    R-cluster 
Requires:         R-CRAN-dplyr 
Requires:         R-cluster 

%description
Implement the methods proposed by Ahmad & Dey (2007)
<doi:10.1016/j.datak.2007.03.016> in calculating the dissimilarity matrix
at the presence of mixed attributes. This Package includes functions to
discretize quantitative variables, calculate conditional probability for
each pair of attribute values, distance between every pair of attribute
values, significance of attributes, calculate dissimilarity between each
pair of objects.

